"children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Contrae esfínter interno","guid":"qFwp0QO0gE0PqVpI0OIz8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"PARASIMPÁTICO (S2-S4)\\N→ nervio pélvico","guid":"2mYeJbvGEov8RtEMOvyGNQ","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Contrae detrusor (ACh → receptores M3)","guid":"WsVdsXEX20nAIHdt6pDrAg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Abre esfínter interno","guid":"x8AChYZD9570e91kYrvSXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"13","text":"SOMÁTICO \\N→ nervio pudendo S2-S4","guid":"rURUrAzf2j3lmT-9suBqFg","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Control voluntario esfínter externo","guid":"a9EW1vt139BH1wDiW_btzw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"STUI como Marcador\\Nde Fragilidad","guid":"j06j2_1G3NnDO-YUA-pUYw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Clasificación\\Npor fase","guid":"Mi7IwPun7LRRD34sYgFFzA","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Almacenamiento → urgencia, poliaquiuria (>8/día), nicturia, incontinencia","guid":"7yDzDEqxRmtDUPdZ0PAuww","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"Vaciamiento → chorro débil, intermitencia, latencia, disuria","guid":"PKuoroYWPE91kknRDfSRPw","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"Post-miccional → goteo, sensación vaciado incompleto","guid":"w5foMTkgXDkPRyNX38vYhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"Relación STUI-Fragilidad-Caídas\\N(CÍRCULO VICIOSO)","guid":"pRbRLLGW3t2hVlLf0GCPoA","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Urgencia urinaria → altera velocidad marcha","guid":"wT0pHAaiCAPTdFwszlgb4w","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Pasos más cortos + mayor variabilidad","guid":"bkmz-V6fmB7UV_WsSAUuHw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Posición flexionada → desplaza centro gravedad","guid":"vdyXXDQYTlmNtdE_nNRx1A","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"→ **↑ RIESGO DE CAÍDAS**","guid":"_rQAuqj3pKd0YK6AojAe2w","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"22","text":"Evidencia estadística","guid":"IZ8OyaQRIc_98KUhFTFLEw","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Urge-incontinencia ≥1/semana → **OR 1.26** caídas","guid":"CgS7LefZ665fuRWwBrxgig","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Urgencia urinaria → **RR 1.7** caídas","guid":"ntIV-W_GzBBvUNK-IMtH6g","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Incontinencia urinaria → **RR 1.9** caídas","guid":"yzs6m6MOvYpTexWOg55Djw","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"22","text":"Impacto\\Nde nicturia","guid":"c32ESogga_dDGvepDKo6Tg","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"46% caídas nocturnas relacionadas con ir al baño","guid":"Qg0-118PpNHPSJiq1gOlYA","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Cualquier fractura → **OR 2.2**","guid":"80Z3hxSAZMCMc1KhKnDUbQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Fractura de cadera → **OR 1.4**","guid":"WrOvbUB2hduNRFH_E9k0DA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"0","text":"RETENCIÓN AGUDA DE\\NORINA (RAO/POUR)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Definición","guid":"oUgAbNrEoVOrPHVP8Q2Vww","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Incapacidad súbita de vaciar vejiga","guid":"jGCshxAGSOb4RIFUu36_9A","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Distensión vesical + volumen residual >300-400 mL","guid":"ktstbAxdYx2uvsHe2W8zfA","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Requiere cateterización","guid":"D7vgDHMM-0nk4eJEG4PWCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"Incidencia en fx cadera → **11. 1-51.3%** (amplio rango)","guid":"mjYhGt_nQ5Be4qCgkjHl_A","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"40","text":"Criterios diagnósticos\\N(POUR)","guid":"cFfvD4lsYQlrvlqODN6e4A","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"CLÍNICOS","guid":"JxVed8MGYBn_z1TtZNCbSg","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Malestar + sensación vejiga llena + vejiga palpable","guid":"k1FwIEJQMKdDSby5217sgg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Incapacidad orinar con distensión vesical","guid":"pL-HpB0sBeys9yKfSewe8Q","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"Volumen >400 mL con vejiga palpable","guid":"i1Xjc0fLcceSJl689dT7Nw","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"No micción >12h post-anestesia con >500 mL drenados","guid":"VT_CfCLmRuHiO-zYEJ3tpA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"No micción 8h tras cirugía o retiro Foley","guid":"pGbUeajz_qofwUr3WsBnOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"46","text":"ULTRASONIDO\\N(Bladder Scan)","guid":"AmBtR5_nfHuddHwUu_h_kg","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Incapacidad orinar + volumen vesical >500-600 mL","guid":"PESe3CtmxCoDKXy-3fKbCg","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Volumen residual >500 mL","guid":"_kRALMEUdg9kYmgOKdv65g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"40","text":"Factores de\\NRiesgo","guid":"2U8sUkXnXDc5mZhXUNnEuw","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"PREOPERATORIOS","guid":"CP8mir2-in487mQHuClSzA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Edad >50 años → **riesgo ↑12.4 veces**","guid":"dSI6X5Jv0RtDjhSOK87s0Q","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Sexo masculino (4.7% vs 2.9% mujeres)","guid":"_pk3a_WbAH61uRxflB0KDQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Síntomas obstructivos previos (HBP) → usar IPSS","guid":"3me0m3HxvOKiRzf-a7HacA","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"IPSS ≥8 → **OR 9. 3** (p<0.001)","guid":"Loskf-yZCx6OOTxRUTfIsA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"Cirugía pélvica/anorrectal previa","guid":"tEbd_7k2u7x9M-yyYJF-yQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"57","text":"Enfermedad neurológica (ACV, Parkinson, neuropatía DM)","guid":"TR-RcCyXNNOth7Lxr7BSTg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"57","text":"Medicación → alfa/beta bloqueadores","guid":"Z9ie6JVeI9mfmpcaSgP_-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"56","text":"INTRAOPERATORIOS","guid":"S9LI2unw5FQx13OD-oSRkg","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Fluidos IV ≥750 mL → **↑ riesgo x2.3**","guid":"RlWJIyMCh4aZXXJj2xB4Vg","children"