":"jvm_BqiCD6TXkeVdWlr6rA","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"↓ transfusión (39% vs 45%)","guid":"BK2ftfaNYcgytdZCtvPVKA","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"252","text":"↓ complicaciones globales","guid":"dF36H3UhqS66WCz8TNAC9g","children":[]}]},{"id":"255","parent":"251","text":"GENERAL\\Nfavorece","guid":"qFtd0bE_gZ4uqk6JtGt4LA","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"↓ ITU en un estudio (5. 76% vs 8.87%)","guid":"S3rL6VLvJ2QVTJvlzUTcyQ","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"255","text":"↓ EP (0.31% vs 0.96%)","guid":"b2kvFmfEObFAV5-rWpVVrQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"251","text":"DATOS CONTRADICTORIOS\\N(Morgan 2020 UK)","guid":"2piwPZq5Img3SvjFr60dCg","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"Espinal PROTECTOR para ITU → OR 0.72 (IC 0.61-0.84)","guid":"TYziZaKSFBt5luPRWCroMQ","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"General PROTECTOR para infección respiratoria","guid":"pztHwvM0pvrndlRfgi_GrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"251","text":"→ **INDIVIDUALIZAR DECISIÓN**","guid":"Qd2UAHMk09FSpuNPiq3TtA","children":[]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"244","text":"Impacto funcionalidad a 1 año\\N(Hellman-Bronstein)","guid":"_k2HtIqmFBL7JHiXTkUbUA","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"Edad 80-89 años → OR 2. 0 mayor asistencia","guid":"87qUF4Xcm9CryAkuvRNAQw","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"Edad ≥90 años → OR 4.3","guid":"Tuy0Xr-UebFnCxW2k8gW2A","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"262","text":"ASA 3-5 → OR 1.67","guid":"eB12DCQplSHA4KjUxF89yQ","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"262","text":"Trastorno cognitivo → OR 2. 87","guid":"Yn_mZtzUZcA_SmKDmqF-rA","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"262","text":"Nivel dependencia previo → OR 3.61-17.0","guid":"gHEBBgiT-Eklh7ygWOALNw","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"262","text":"**Retiro catéter diferido → OR 1.67**","guid":"Ph3y0nto_HP-RwtGmxxR0g","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"262","text":"Incontinencia uro-fecal previa → OR 2.4","guid":"ZAXZUXVK0lWPQv97laal3w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"0","text":"PERLAS\\NCLÍNICAS ⭐","guid":"6-cYKlJ5kby3TemG6Fe2ag","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"El INTESTINO AFECTA la VEJIGA → fecaloma OR 4.78 para RAO; no manejar vejiga sin manejar intestino","guid":"qvBneMdRgZQJMJB1ntF0JQ","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"ITU preoperatoria → triplica riesgo ISO (OR ~2.4-2.8); descartar/tratar antes de cirugía","guid":"hGwPHKOOGjouAm2EyrKSRQ","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"270","text":"Historia SEPSIS previa → FR más potente para ITU post-fx (OR 7.13) > sondaje","guid":"fwJltD8KDChRYS97ZBE_Rw","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"270","text":"SONDA = arma doble filo → ↑ ITU x4 (OR 3.8) + retiro tardío ↑ IU x2 (OR 2. 33); objetivo 24-48h","guid":"grepLJkIpknlj6sgXpWV_w","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"270","text":"Intervención educativa simple (hábitos + llamada telefónica) → **NNT 4** para prevenir IU; bajo costo/alto impacto","guid":"_HShkXVPUM_nUT54WqHZKA","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"270","text":"CÍRCULO VICIOSO → IU duplica caídas (OR 1.94) → fracturas → agravan IU/dependencia","guid":"zZ_CS_usnJkKUYI23mmsyg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"270","text":"DELIRIUM-ITU → asociación bidireccional (OR 2.66); en cambio mental agudo descartar ITU y RAO","guid":"cNpueUdI2DY0pW2LBmkUMg","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"270","text":"Fluidos IV >750 mL → duplican riesgo RAO (x2.3); ser juicioso con fluidoterapia","guid":"TObhA8uOLLdHErTZKlD4Vw","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"270","text":"Anestesia espinal bloquea detrusor por horas (hasta 8h retorno sensitivo S3) → RR 14 vs bloqueo nervioso","guid":"WVHeQU_kZNaFph-nWvXCbA","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"270","text":"Post-retiro sin micción → Bladder Scan ANTES de re-cateterizar (criterio >500-600 mL)","guid":"rCEH20qK4IeEAqzmUU8B3Q","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"270","text":"IPSS ≥8 preoperatorio → OR 9.3 para POUR; útil para estratificar riesgo","guid":"Xdjtnn2tuz89j1_L-g_hJw","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"270","text":"Anticolinérgicos → OR 11.9 para POUR; revisar/suspender previo cirugía si posible","guid":"OCqvhzIYmXj4nKODceR7tQ","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"270","text":"Movilización precoz 24h → protege contra POUR (OR 6.5 si no logra salir de cama)","guid":"i9D3RwCopuPgm6jPwTfVIQ","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"270","text":"“Pull the Foley” (enfermería empoderada) → ↓30% ITU intrahospitalaria","guid":"deyGKJxqx5aKQAKbe6584w","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"270","text":"En demencia → disconfort urinario = cambios conductuales (agitación, delirium hipoactivo), no quejas verbales","guid":"P460eIypnJcvTCA2kj12Uw","children":[]}]},{"id":"286","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"1. Cacciatore S, Ferrara MC, Iuorio MS, et al. Urinary Catheterization Management in Older Adults with Hip Fracture: A Systematic Review. JAMDA. 2025;26:105410.","guid":"r4_aSgbNEuJfvGx5a56AxQ","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"286","text":"2. Toro Lara CP. Guía: Complicaciones Urinarias en Fractura de Cadera. Residencia Geriatría USS, Rotación Ortogeriatría. Noviembre 2025.","guid":"L3xZdYSsQzKjS-o1CXDc6g","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"286","text":"3. Barbagelata F. Guía: Complicaciones Urinarias Agudas y Subagudas en Paciente con Fractura de Cadera. Residencia Geriatría USACH. Mayo 2024.","guid":"MsGPQuQ8LE_F676wd3u1wQ","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"286","text":"4. Xia J, Zhao D, Hu Y, et al. Incidence and risk factors for postoperative urinary retention in older patients with hip fracture: a scoping review. BMJ Open. 2025;15(9):e100368. doi:10.1136/bmjopen-2025-100368","guid":"Jih-q5QJ5SyZpze55L0AWw","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"286","text":"5. Tantigate D, Jansatjawan N, Adulkasem N, et al. Risk factors for postoperative urinary retention in fragility hip fracture patients: a prospective study. BMC Geriatr. 2024;24(1):483. doi:10.1186/s12877-024-05101-2","guid":"ecA-MYjojregIY40a-bmlQ","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"286","text":"6. Wang et al. Meta-análisis factores de riesgo ITU en fractura de cadera. 2024.","guid":"dm9rRzZbZMXSIn01N62KEA","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"286","text":"7. Teng et al. Impact of fecal impaction on urinary retention in hip fracture. 2021.","guid":"y61uqbLGth-OAWwCiqandQ","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"286","text":"8. Córcoles-Jiménez MP et al. Educational intervention for urinary incontinence after hip fracture (RCT). 2021.","guid":"FKxoFIWBpFKlQzFMVDo5SQ","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"286","text":"9. Hellman-Bronstein et al. Factors associated with urinary incontinence subtypes post hip fracture.","guid":"yQKP8F2NVd9Kw4s0H64w0A","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"286","text":"10. Frodin M et al. Nurse-led bladder scan protocol in hip fracture. Suecia, 2022.","guid":"X6BBeycHtrR_beUZKQeWkA","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"286","text":"11. Konda SR et al. “Pull the Foley” policy impact on CAUTI. USA, 2020.","guid":"v4kWDAs0nawGsdz-niNEYQ","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"286","text":"12. Fields AC et al. Spinal vs general anesthesia complications in hip fracture. ACS-NSQIP, 2015.","guid":"Zg9oq3CbrcLHUatrZBteaw","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"286","text":"13. Morgan L et al. Anesthesia type and complications (UK database). 2020.","guid":"DGL3_-LuA6C3ZXbDrCgGSA","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"286","text":"14. Suen et al. UTI and surgical site infection risk. J Hosp Infect. 2023.","guid":"pUeMN4M5EkLaZpbA9tq2qg","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"286","text":"15. Crouser N et al. UTI at time of surgery outcomes (NSQIP). 2015-2016.","guid":"CQ41RiI_5UMLJH6CaHebVg","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":301,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto COMPLICACIONES URINARIAS EN FRACTURA DE CADERA-2026","id":"map_1523","resolved_references":[]}